# Rust
/target
**/target
**/*.rs.bk
*.pdb

# Secrets — NEVER commit keys, seeds, or real test vectors
*.seed
*.key
*.pem
*.secret
secrets/
*vector*.local.*
.env
.env.*

# Runtime artifacts
chain-eos.watermark

# Research-lane draft staging (one-door). Drafts live untracked under docs/;
# an adopted finding graduates to docs/ or docs/architecture/ with its own
# STATUS ledger line (as did-autonomi-spec.md did). These pens also hold
# FOR-COUNSEL (legal) and founder-decision drafts (tokenomics, governance
# parameters, peg ratios) the builder must not publish unilaterally.
# Non-destructive: files stay on disk; `git add -f` to adopt a specific one.
docs/findings/
# docs/design/* (not docs/design/) so the exception below can re-include one
# file — git cannot un-ignore a file whose PARENT DIR is excluded.
docs/design/*
# ...except the shared non-value-state spec: it is the ONE canonical home both
# surfaces + Fable's pointers reference, and implementation reads from it. The
# rest of docs/design/ stays a deferred holding pen.
!docs/design/non-value-states.md

# Editor / OS
.DS_Store
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
